<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en" data-theme="light">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8" />
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
  <title>Ella Joy Ignacio | Content Operations & Social Media Support</title>
  <meta name="description" content="Ella Joy Ignacio helps creators, founders, and small teams with YouTube operations, short-form content, thumbnails, website management, admin support, and social media management." />

  <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.googleapis.com">
  <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.gstatic.com" crossorigin>
  <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Inter:wght@400;500;600;700;800&family=Playfair+Display:wght@600;700;800&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
  <link rel="stylesheet" href="https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/font-awesome/6.5.2/css/all.min.css">

  <style>
    :root {
      --bg: #fff9f3;
      --bg-2: #f7eee4;
      --card: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.82);
      --card-solid: #ffffff;
      --text: #34231d;
      --muted: #7d6b5f;
      --border: rgba(102, 77, 61, 0.14);
      --accent: #e88394;
      --accent-2: #9f6bff;
      --accent-soft: rgba(232, 131, 148, 0.14);
      --shadow: 0 24px 70px rgba(79, 48, 36, 0.10);
      --shadow-soft: 0 14px 40px rgba(79, 48, 36, 0.08);
      --radius-xl: 34px;
      --radius-lg: 24px;
      --radius-md: 18px;
      --max: 1160px;
      --transition: 240ms ease;
    }

    html[data-theme="dark"] {
      --bg: #0d0b0b;
      --bg-2: #171313;
      --card: rgba(28, 22, 22, 0.80);
      --card-solid: #171313;
      --text: #fff4ec;
      --muted: #b9a99f;
      --border: rgba(255, 238, 226, 0.12);
      --accent: #ff9aaa;
      --accent-2: #b795ff;
      --accent-soft: rgba(255, 154, 170, 0.14);
      --shadow: 0 24px 70px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.38);
      --shadow-soft: 0 14px 40px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.26);
    }

    * { box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0; padding: 0; }
    html { scroll-behavior: smooth; scroll-padding-top: 96px; }
    body {
      font-family: Inter, system-ui, sans-serif;
      background:
        radial-gradient(circle at top left, var(--accent-soft), transparent 30%),
        radial-gradient(circle at 85% 12%, rgba(159,107,255,.12), transparent 28%),
        var(--bg);
      color: var(--text);
      line-height: 1.6;
      overflow-x: hidden;
      transition: background var(--transition), color var(--transition);
    }
    a { color: inherit; text-decoration: none; }
    img { max-width: 100%; display: block; }
    .wrap { width: min(var(--max), calc(100% - 40px)); margin: 0 auto; }

    header {
      position: sticky;
      top: 0;
      z-index: 50;
      backdrop-filter: blur(18px);
      background: color-mix(in srgb, var(--bg) 78%, transparent);
      border-bottom: 1px solid var(--border);
    }
    nav { min-height: 76px; display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: space-between; gap: 20px; }
    .brand { font-family: "Playfair Display", serif; font-size: 24px; font-weight: 800; letter-spacing: -0.03em; }
    .brand span { color: var(--accent); font-style: italic; }
    .nav-links { display: flex; gap: 24px; align-items: center; color: var(--muted); font-size: 14px; font-weight: 700; }
    .nav-links a:hover { color: var(--accent); }
    .nav-actions { display: flex; align-items: center; gap: 12px; }
    .theme-toggle {
      border: 1px solid var(--border);
      background: var(--card);
      color: var(--text);
      border-radius: 999px;
      padding: 10px 13px;
      cursor: pointer;
      display: inline-flex;
      align-items: center;
      gap: 8px;
      font-weight: 800;
      box-shadow: var(--shadow-soft);
      transition: transform var(--transition), border-color var(--transition), background var(--transition);
    }
    .theme-toggle:hover { transform: translateY(-2px); border-color: var(--accent); }

    .btn {
      display: inline-flex;
      align-items: center;
      justify-content: center;
      gap: 10px;
      border-radius: 999px;
      padding: 13px 20px;
      font-weight: 800;
      border: 1px solid transparent;
      transition: transform var(--transition), box-shadow var(--transition), border-color var(--transition), background var(--transition);
      cursor: pointer;
    }
    .btn:hover { transform: translateY(-2px); }
    .btn-primary { background: var(--text); color: var(--bg); box-shadow: var(--shadow-soft); }
    .btn-primary:hover { background: var(--accent); color: #fff; }
    .btn-secondary { border-color: var(--border); background: var(--card); color: var(--text); }
    .btn-secondary:hover { border-color: var(--accent); }

    section { padding: 96px 0; }
    .section-tag { display: inline-flex; align-items: center; gap: 8px; color: var(--accent); font-size: 12px; font-weight: 900; letter-spacing: .12em; text-transform: uppercase; margin-bottom: 14px; }
    h1, h2 { font-family: "Playfair Display", serif; letter-spacing: -0.05em; line-height: 1.05; }
    h1 { font-size: clamp(44px, 8vw, 86px); max-width: 780px; }
    h2 { font-size: clamp(34px, 5vw, 58px); max-width: 780px; }
    h3 { line-height: 1.2; }
    .lead { color: var(--muted); font-size: clamp(17px, 2vw, 20px); max-width: 760px; margin-top: 20px; }
    .accent { color: var(--accent); font-style: italic; }

    .hero { padding: 110px 0 80px; }
    .hero-grid { display: grid; grid-template-columns: 1.1fr .9fr; gap: 56px; align-items: center; }
    .hero-actions { display: flex; gap: 14px; flex-wrap: wrap; margin: 34px 0 22px; }

    .hero-mini-badges {
      display: flex;
      flex-wrap: wrap;
      gap: 10px;
      margin: 8px 0 30px;
    }
    .hero-mini-badges span {
      display: inline-flex;
      align-items: center;
      gap: 8px;
      border: 1px solid var(--border);
      background: color-mix(in srgb, var(--card-solid) 86%, transparent);
      color: var(--text);
      border-radius: 999px;
      padding: 10px 15px;
      font-size: 13px;
      font-weight: 900;
      box-shadow: var(--shadow-soft);
      transition: transform var(--transition), border-color var(--transition), background var(--transition);
    }
    .hero-mini-badges span:hover {
      transform: translateY(-3px);
      border-color: var(--accent);
      background: var(--accent-soft);
    }

    .proof-row { display: grid; grid-template-columns: repeat(3, 1fr); gap: 14px; margin-top: 28px; }
    .proof-card { border: 1px solid var(--border); background: var(--card); border-radius: var(--radius-md); padding: 20px; box-shadow: var(--shadow-soft); }
    .proof-card strong { display: block; font-size: 26px; font-weight: 900; }
    .proof-card span { color: var(--muted); font-size: 13px; font-weight: 700; }
    .hero-visual { position: relative; }
    .profile-card {
      border: 1px solid var(--border);
      background: linear-gradient(145deg, var(--card), color-mix(in srgb, var(--accent-soft) 45%, transparent));
      border-radius: var(--radius-xl);
      padding: 24px;
      box-shadow: var(--shadow);
      min-height: 520px;
      display: grid;
      align-content: space-between;
      overflow: hidden;
      position: relative;
    }
    .profile-card::before {
      content: "";
      position: absolute;
      width: 230px;
      height: 230px;
      border-radius: 50%;
      background: var(--accent-soft);
      top: -80px;
      right: -70px;
    }
    .photo-placeholder {
      border: 1px dashed var(--border);
      border-radius: 26px;
      height: 330px;
      display: grid;
      place-items: center;
      color: var(--muted);
      background: color-mix(in srgb, var(--card-solid) 70%, transparent);
      position: relative;
      z-index: 1;
      text-align: center;
      padding: 20px;
      font-weight: 800;
    }
    .floating-note { display: none; }

    .about { background: color-mix(in srgb, var(--bg-2) 82%, transparent); border-block: 1px solid var(--border); }
    .about-grid { display: grid; grid-template-columns: .9fr 1.1fr; gap: 38px; align-items: start; }
    .snapshot-card {
      border: 1px solid var(--border);
      background: var(--card);
      border-radius: var(--radius-xl);
      box-shadow: var(--shadow);
      padding: 26px;
      position: sticky;
      top: 102px;
    }
    .snapshot-head { display: flex; gap: 18px; align-items: center; margin-bottom: 24px; }
    .avatar-placeholder { width: 86px; height: 86px; border-radius: 26px; display: grid; place-items: center; border: 1px dashed var(--border); color: var(--muted); background: var(--accent-soft); font-size: 11px; text-align: center; font-weight: 800; }
    .snapshot-head h3 { font-size: 22px; }
    .snapshot-head p { color: var(--muted); font-weight: 700; font-size: 14px; }
    .snapshot-grid { display: grid; grid-template-columns: repeat(2, 1fr); gap: 12px; }
    .mini-card { border: 1px solid var(--border); border-radius: 18px; padding: 16px; background: color-mix(in srgb, var(--card-solid) 78%, transparent); transition: transform var(--transition), border-color var(--transition); }
    .mini-card:hover { transform: translateY(-3px); border-color: var(--accent); }
    .mini-card i { color: var(--accent); margin-bottom: 10px; }
    .mini-card small { color: var(--muted); display: block; font-weight: 800; text-transform: uppercase; letter-spacing: .08em; font-size: 10px; }
    .mini-card strong { display: block; font-size: 14px; margin-top: 4px; }
    .about-copy { border: 1px solid var(--border); border-radius: var(--radius-xl); background: var(--card); padding: 36px; box-shadow: var(--shadow-soft); }
    .about-copy p { color: var(--muted); margin-top: 18px; font-size: 17px; }

    .services-grid { display: grid; grid-template-columns: repeat(3, 1fr); gap: 18px; margin-top: 44px; }
    .service-card { border: 1px solid var(--border); background: var(--card); border-radius: var(--radius-lg); padding: 24px; box-shadow: var(--shadow-soft); min-height: 230px; transition: transform var(--transition), border-color var(--transition); }
    .service-card:hover { transform: translateY(-5px); border-color: var(--accent); }
    .icon-chip { width: 48px; height: 48px; border-radius: 16px; background: var(--accent-soft); color: var(--accent); display: grid; place-items: center; margin-bottom: 20px; font-size: 20px; }
    .service-card h3 { font-size: 18px; margin-bottom: 10px; }
    .service-card p { color: var(--muted); font-size: 14.5px; }

    .workspace { background: color-mix(in srgb, var(--bg-2) 82%, transparent); border-block: 1px solid var(--border); }
    .workspace-grid { display: grid; grid-template-columns: repeat(2, 1fr); gap: 24px; margin-top: 44px; }
    .case-card { border: 1px solid var(--border); background: var(--card); border-radius: var(--radius-xl); padding: 24px; box-shadow: var(--shadow); overflow: hidden; }
    .preview { border-radius: 24px; overflow: hidden; border: 1px solid var(--border); min-height: 285px; background: #101010; margin-bottom: 24px; position: relative; }
    .youtube-preview { background: linear-gradient(145deg, #111, #2a171a); display: grid; align-content: end; }
    .youtube-preview::before { content: "Add James channel thumbnail here"; color: rgba(255,255,255,.5); position: absolute; inset: 0; display: grid; place-items: center; font-weight: 800; font-size: 13px; }
    .play { position: absolute; width: 68px; height: 68px; border-radius: 50%; background: #ff0033; color: #fff; display: grid; place-items: center; left: 50%; top: 44%; transform: translate(-50%, -50%); box-shadow: 0 20px 50px rgba(255,0,51,.34); z-index: 2; }
    .yt-bar { position: relative; z-index: 2; background: rgba(0,0,0,.78); padding: 18px; display: flex; gap: 12px; align-items: center; color: #fff; }
    .yt-avatar { width: 42px; height: 42px; border-radius: 50%; background: var(--accent); }
    .yt-bar span { display: block; color: rgba(255,255,255,.62); font-size: 12px; }
    .website-preview { background: #090d12; display: flex; flex-direction: column; }
    .browser-top { background: #f1eee9; padding: 12px; display: flex; align-items: center; gap: 9px; }
    .dot { width: 10px; height: 10px; background: #b8ada4; border-radius: 50%; }
    .url { margin-left: 8px; background: #fff; border-radius: 10px; padding: 7px 14px; color: #111; font-size: 12px; font-weight: 900; flex: 1; }
    .website-body { flex: 1; display: grid; place-items: center; color: #56f18b; text-align: center; font-family: ui-monospace, SFMono-Regular, Menlo, monospace; font-weight: 800; padding: 24px; }
    .case-card h3 { font-size: 24px; margin-bottom: 8px; }
    .case-card p { color: var(--muted); margin: 14px 0 22px; }
    .case-actions { display: flex; gap: 12px; flex-wrap: wrap; }

    .bento-grid { display: grid; grid-template-columns: 1.25fr .75fr 1fr; gap: 18px; margin-top: 44px; }
    .bento { border: 1px solid var(--border); background: var(--card); border-radius: var(--radius-lg); padding: 24px; min-height: 180px; box-shadow: var(--shadow-soft); transition: transform var(--transition), border-color var(--transition); }
    .bento:hover { transform: translateY(-5px); border-color: var(--accent); }
    .bento.big { grid-row: span 2; min-height: 378px; background: linear-gradient(145deg, var(--card), var(--accent-soft)); }
    .bento.wide { grid-column: span 2; }
    .bento i { color: var(--accent); font-size: 24px; margin-bottom: 18px; }
    .bento h3 { font-size: 18px; margin-bottom: 9px; }
    .bento p { color: var(--muted); font-size: 14px; }

    .experience-list { display: grid; gap: 18px; margin-top: 44px; }
    .exp-card { display: grid; grid-template-columns: 270px 1fr; gap: 28px; border: 1px solid var(--border); background: var(--card); border-radius: var(--radius-lg); padding: 26px; box-shadow: var(--shadow-soft); }
    .exp-card h3 { font-size: 20px; }
    .exp-card p { color: var(--muted); margin-bottom: 16px; }
    .tags { display: flex; flex-wrap: wrap; gap: 8px; }
    .tags span { border: 1px solid var(--border); background: color-mix(in srgb, var(--bg-2) 70%, transparent); border-radius: 999px; padding: 7px 12px; color: var(--muted); font-size: 12px; font-weight: 800; }

    .tools { background: color-mix(in srgb, var(--bg-2) 82%, transparent); border-block: 1px solid var(--border); }
    .tool-groups { display: grid; gap: 22px; margin-top: 44px; }
    .tool-group { border: 1px solid var(--border); background: var(--card); border-radius: var(--radius-lg); padding: 24px; box-shadow: var(--shadow-soft); }
    .tool-group h3 { margin-bottom: 16px; }
    .tool-row { display: flex; flex-wrap: wrap; gap: 12px; }
    .tool { display: inline-flex; align-items: center; gap: 10px; border: 1px solid var(--border); background: color-mix(in srgb, var(--card-solid) 82%, transparent); border-radius: 15px; padding: 12px 15px; font-weight: 900; font-size: 14px; }
    .tool i { color: var(--accent); min-width: 18px; text-align: center; }

    .process-grid { display: grid; grid-template-columns: repeat(3, 1fr); gap: 18px; margin-top: 44px; counter-reset: step; }
    .process-card { counter-increment: step; border: 1px solid var(--border); background: var(--card); border-radius: var(--radius-lg); padding: 24px; box-shadow: var(--shadow-soft); position: relative; overflow: hidden; }
    .process-card::before { content: "0" counter(step); font-family: "Playfair Display", serif; position: absolute; right: 18px; top: 8px; color: var(--accent-soft); font-size: 70px; font-weight: 900; line-height: 1; }
    .process-card h3 { position: relative; font-size: 18px; margin-bottom: 10px; }
    .process-card p { position: relative; color: var(--muted); font-size: 14.5px; }

    .cta { text-align: center; }
    .cta-box { border: 1px solid var(--border); background: linear-gradient(145deg, var(--card), var(--accent-soft)); border-radius: var(--radius-xl); padding: 56px 28px; box-shadow: var(--shadow); }
    .cta-box h2, .cta-box .lead { margin-inline: auto; }
    .cta-actions { display: flex; justify-content: center; gap: 14px; flex-wrap: wrap; margin-top: 32px; }
    footer { padding: 52px 0 32px; border-top: 1px solid var(--border); background: var(--bg-2); text-align: center; }
    .socials { display: flex; justify-content: center; gap: 12px; margin: 26px 0; }
    .socials a { width: 48px; height: 48px; border: 1px solid var(--border); background: var(--card); border-radius: 50%; display: grid; place-items: center; color: var(--text); transition: transform var(--transition), background var(--transition); }
    .socials a:hover { transform: translateY(-4px); background: var(--accent); color: #fff; }
    .footer-note { color: var(--muted); font-size: 13px; }

    .reveal { opacity: 0; transform: translateY(28px); transition: opacity 700ms ease, transform 700ms ease; }
    .reveal.is-visible { opacity: 1; transform: translateY(0); }
    .stagger > * { opacity: 0; transform: translateY(18px); transition: opacity 650ms ease, transform 650ms ease; }
    .stagger.is-visible > * { opacity: 1; transform: translateY(0); }
    .stagger.is-visible > *:nth-child(2) { transition-delay: 80ms; }
    .stagger.is-visible > *:nth-child(3) { transition-delay: 140ms; }
    .stagger.is-visible > *:nth-child(4) { transition-delay: 200ms; }
    .stagger.is-visible > *:nth-child(5) { transition-delay: 260ms; }
    .stagger.is-visible > *:nth-child(6) { transition-delay: 320ms; }

    @media (prefers-reduced-motion: reduce) {
      *, *::before, *::after { scroll-behavior: auto !important; transition: none !important; animation: none !important; }
      .reveal, .stagger > * { opacity: 1 !important; transform: none !important; }
    }

    @media (max-width: 980px) {
      .nav-links { display: none; }
      .hero-grid, .about-grid, .workspace-grid, .exp-card { grid-template-columns: 1fr; }
      .snapshot-card { position: relative; top: 0; }
      .services-grid, .process-grid { grid-template-columns: repeat(2, 1fr); }
      .bento-grid { grid-template-columns: repeat(2, 1fr); }
      .bento.big, .bento.wide { grid-column: auto; grid-row: auto; min-height: 180px; }
      .profile-card { min-height: 440px; }
    }
    @media (max-width: 680px) {
      .wrap { width: min(100% - 28px, var(--max)); }
      nav { min-height: 70px; }
      .brand { font-size: 20px; }
      .nav-actions .btn { display: none; }
      section { padding: 72px 0; }
      .hero { padding-top: 76px; }
      .proof-row, .snapshot-grid, .services-grid, .workspace-grid, .bento-grid, .process-grid { grid-template-columns: 1fr; }
      .hero-mini-badges span { width: 100%; justify-content: center; }
      .about-copy, .snapshot-card, .case-card, .cta-box { padding: 22px; }
      .preview { min-height: 230px; }
      .floating-note { display: none; }
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <header>
    <nav class="wrap">
      <a href="#top" class="brand">Ella Joy <span>Ignacio</span></a>
      <div class="nav-links">
        <a href="#about">About</a>
        <a href="#services">Services</a>
        <a href="#work">Client Work</a>
        <a href="#tools">Tools</a>
        <a href="#process">Process</a>
      </div>
      <div class="nav-actions">
        <button class="theme-toggle" id="themeToggle" type="button" aria-label="Toggle light and dark mode"><i class="fa-solid fa-moon"></i><span>Dark</span></button>
        <a href="#contact" class="btn btn-primary">Work With Me</a>
      </div>
    </nav>
  </header>

  <main id="top">
    <section class="hero reveal">
      <div class="wrap hero-grid">
        <div>
          <div class="section-tag"><i class="fa-solid fa-sparkles"></i> Content Operations & Social Media Support</div>
          <h1>I help creators stay <span class="accent">consistent online</span> without doing everything alone.</h1>
          <p class="lead">I support YouTube creators, founders, and small teams with Shorts, thumbnails, carousels, website updates, blog uploads, email campaigns, admin work, and social media management.</p>
          <div class="hero-actions">
            <a class="btn btn-primary" href="#contact"><i class="fa-solid fa-paper-plane"></i> Work With Me</a>
            <a class="btn btn-secondary" href="#work"><i class="fa-solid fa-play"></i> View Client Work</a>
          </div>

          <div class="hero-mini-badges">
            <span><i class="fa-brands fa-youtube"></i> YouTube Operations</span>
            <span><i class="fa-solid fa-globe"></i> Website Management</span>
            <span><i class="fa-solid fa-share-nodes"></i> Social Media</span>
            <span><i class="fa-solid fa-envelope-open-text"></i> Email Marketing</span>
          </div>

          <div class="proof-row stagger">
            <div class="proof-card"><strong>100+</strong><span>short-form clips supported</span></div>
            <div class="proof-card"><strong>5+</strong><span>content areas managed</span></div>
            <div class="proof-card"><strong>Remote</strong><span>creator & admin support</span></div>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="hero-visual">
          <div class="profile-card">
            <div class="photo-placeholder">Add Ella headshot here</div>
            <div>
              <h3>Behind-the-scenes content support for busy creators.</h3>
              <p style="color: var(--muted); margin-top: 8px;">You create. I help organize, repurpose, publish, and manage the content system.</p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="about reveal" id="about">
      <div class="wrap about-grid">
        <aside class="snapshot-card">
          <div class="snapshot-head">
            <div class="avatar-placeholder">Add<br>photo</div>
            <div>
              <h3>Ella Joy B. Ignacio</h3>
              <p>Content Operations & Social Media Support</p>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="snapshot-grid stagger">
            <div class="mini-card"><i class="fa-solid fa-location-dot"></i><small>Based in</small><strong>BGC, Philippines</strong></div>
            <div class="mini-card"><i class="fa-solid fa-graduation-cap"></i><small>Education</small><strong>BSBA Management</strong></div>
            <div class="mini-card"><i class="fa-brands fa-youtube"></i><small>Focus</small><strong>YouTube Support</strong></div>
            <div class="mini-card"><i class="fa-solid fa-globe"></i><small>Skill</small><strong>Website Management</strong></div>
            <div class="mini-card"><i class="fa-solid fa-headset"></i><small>Experience</small><strong>Admin & CSR</strong></div>
            <div class="mini-card"><i class="fa-solid fa-laptop"></i><small>Setup</small><strong>Remote-Friendly</strong></div>
          </div>
        </aside>
        <div class="about-copy">
          <div class="section-tag">About Me Snapshot</div>
          <h2>Hi, I’m Ella Joy B. Ignacio</h2>
          <p>I’m a 24-year-old content operations and social media support specialist based in BGC, Philippines. I graduated with a Bachelor of Science in Business Administration major in Management, and I’ve built experience across YouTube operations, social media management, website support, admin work, customer service, and digital marketing.</p>
          <p>I work behind the scenes to help creators, founders, and businesses stay consistent online — from creating Shorts and thumbnails to managing content calendars, uploading blogs, supporting email campaigns, and organizing daily workflows.</p>
